# PaymentCardReadResult.ReadOutcome.failure

**Case**

The read failed somehow, the card data may not contain all requested tags.

## Declaration

```swift
case failure
```

## Getting the read outcome

- **PaymentCardReadResult.ReadOutcome.success**: The read was successful.
- **PaymentCardReadResult.ReadOutcome.cardDeclined**: The card declined this transaction.
